    "## Dataset 2 \n",
    "Columns: Patient ID, Name, Age, Body Temperature(F), Heart rate(bpm),\n",
    "Systolic Blood Pressure(mm Hg), Diastolic Blood Pressure(mm Hg), BMI(kg/m 2),\n",
    "Blood Glucose(HbA1c), Blood Glucose(Fasting hour-mg/dl), Status\n",
    "\n",
    "Note: Blood Glucose(HbA1c) and Blood Glucose(Fasting) are not equivalent to BS (mmol/L fasting glucose)\n",
    "used in the training dataset and are therefore excluded from the shared feature set."
   ]
